{"title":"New DC Rainmaker Cycling & Running Gear Available!","link":"https://www.dcrainmaker.com/2024/09/rainmaker-cycling-running-gear-kits-available.html","date":1726223071000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-28-1-720x480.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-28-1-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-28-1-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-28-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-28-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-28-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-28-1-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></p>\n<p>The most astute of followers have noticed over the course of the year I’ve been trialing some new <a href=\"https://www.ciovita.com/collections/dc-rainmaker\">DC Rainmaker branded cycling and running gear</a>. It’s been a number of years since the last cycling kit was available, and plenty of you have been asking for something to be available again. Not only that, but also a running technical shirt as well!</p>\n<p>We partnered with CIOVITA for these kits, which makes high-end cycling and running kits for many teams, as well as also events like the famed Cape Epic race in Cape Town, South Africa, and more. The <a href=\"https://www.ciovita.com/pages/about-us\">company is based in Cape Town as well</a>, though the kits ship globally with customs pre-paid ahead of time. I’ve been testing kits since back in January, in some cases literally beating the crap out of them to ensure the quality is what I want. We made the kits first available at the DCR Open House back in July, and then expanded it to DCR Supporters shortly after that. Since then many of them have posted to Strava and elsewhere sporting the new goodness!</p>\n\n<a href=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-1-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-1-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-1-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-1-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-1-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-15-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-15-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-15-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-15-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-15-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-15-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-15-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-15-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-19-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-19-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-19-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-19-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-19-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-19-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-19-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-19-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-11-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-11-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-11-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-11-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-11-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-11-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-11-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-12-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-12-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-12-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-12-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-12-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-12-1