eight=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-34-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-34-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-34-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-34-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-34-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-34-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-34-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-38-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-38-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-38-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-38-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-38-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-38-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-38-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-38-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-40-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-40-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-40-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-40-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-40-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-40-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-40-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-40-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-45-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-45-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-45-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-45-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-45-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-45-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-45-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-45-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-16-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-16-300x200.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-16-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-16-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-16-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-16-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-16-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></a>\n\n<p>In short, the <a href=\"https://www.ciovita.com/collections/dc-rainmaker\">first collection includes</a> (both men’s and women’s variants):</p>\n<p>– Cycling jersey<br />\n– Cycling bibs (regular)<br />\n– Cycling cargo bibs<br />\n– Cycling gilet<br />\n– Cycling socks<br />\n– Running technical shirt</p>\n<p>I say ‘collection’, because we’re going to launch some other limited-run styles throughout the year, but this kit is the main DC Rainmaker kit. As well, we hope to add a few cold weather options coming up this fall.</p>\n<p>On the cycling side, the kits are available in a wide range of sizing. Do check the sizing charts listed at the bottom of each page, because as always, it varies by exact product. For example, my wife is wearing a small cycling bib, and a S cycling jersey (seen below) arguably she needs an XS in this style. You can mix and match. Meanwhile, I’m wearing XL of both.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-7-1-720x480.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-7-1-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-7-1-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-7-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-7-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-7-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-7-1-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></p>\n<p>Of course, my favorite part of the new kit is probably the cycling cargo short bib. That’s been amazeballs for me and carrying cameras, drones, and even just nutrition. It’s become my defacto place for both action cams and drones, but on the nutrition front, I find having it there serves as a better reminder.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-35-720x480.jpg\" width=\"334\" height=\"223\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-35-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-35-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-35-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-35-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-35-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-35-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-36-720x480.jpg\" width=\"335\" height=\"223\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-36-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-36-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-36-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-36-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-36-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-36-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></p>\n<p>Finally, over on the running side, the technical shirt is incredibly lightweight. It was a requirement for me to have something for the runners this go around, as many people requested it over the years (heck, including myself).</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-47-720x480.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-47-720x480.jpg 720w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-47-200x133.jpg 200w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-47-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-47-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-47-300x200.jpg 300w, https://media.dcrainmaker.com/images/2024/09/Ciovita_DCRainmaker_July24-47-720x480@2x.jpg 1440w\" /></p>\n<p>Also, when you cannonball in the water post-run, it dries out really quickly in the sun. I mean, just in case that’s a factor in your purchasing decision. I can confirm it’s cannonball-certified.</p>\n<p>Lastly, in terms of logistics, the best part is there are no pre-orders or such. It’s just <strong>instantly available</strong>, at least until initial stock runs out. Ciovita ships globally, and any applicable customs taxes/duties are pre-included in the final price you see. Through all the help of DCR Supporters and those who came to the Open House, we’ve been ensuring no snags in the shipping to many countries around the world. All shipments are done via FedEx or DHL, and typically take 2-3 days to arrive.</p>\n<p>Again, this is a huge difference from the past where you had to pre-order and wait some weeks. This time around, we’ve pre-stocked everything, so you can have instant gratification (well, at least until the first lot sells out – so…ya know, act quick!), but we will continue to re-stock as long as you continue to buy!</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.ciovita.com/collections/dc-rainmaker\">Shop the DC Rainmaker Collection here!!!</a></strong></p>\n<p>Thanks again to everyone who’s given feedback on the designs in testing over the last 6-8 months, as well as those who’ve already purchased the kits. Definitely tag me on social media or Strava if you’re wearing one, so I can share it out!</p>\n<p>Have a great weekend all!</p>","author":"Ray Maker","siteTitle":"DC Rainmaker","siteHash":"32f541eec2062fbf675b0daf837db78b41cd6160cf993de3c4b5e9b44a978706","entryHash":"d5a7c332762769c9cbbc1bc9e59f41626c2ed4fbeb2ce1bcc88dda35451a21b0","category":"Cycling"}